          <p>This project was made when I was in <a href="https://bridgeschool.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bridge school</a>. We formed a team of five, </p>
  				<a class="btn btn-githubg" href="https://github.com/bridge-school/company-cert-frontend" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg class="svg-icon svg-icon__github">
              <use xlink:href="#icon-github"></use>
            </svg>
            <span>View on Github</span>
          </a>
        </div>
  		</div>
  	</div>
