  </section>
  <footer>
    <div class="container container__wide row">
      <div class="two-thirds column">
        <p><small>Made with ❤️ by Coral He, Toronto. 2019<br>
          Icons from <a href="https://thenounproject.com/grega.cresnar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gregor Cresnar</a>.</small></p>
